                "invention-title": [
                    "Substitutive application system for ash hydrogen of thermal power plant",
                    "火电厂灰氢的替代应用系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a replacement application system for grey hydrogen of a thermal power plant, which replaces a hydrogen source of the thermal power plant with new energy hydrogen production, is beneficial to carbon emission reduction of the thermal power plant, assists in realizing an industrial mode of green hydrogen production with green electricity and industrial green hydrogen, and improves the value of the thermal power plant for new energy consumption. And after the hydrogen source is replaced, the existing hydrogen storage tank pressure vessel can be eliminated, and the related detection work of the power plant pressure vessel is reduced. The system comprises: a hydrogen pressure transfer device; a pressure reducing valve group; and a busbar; the hydrogen pressure transfer equipment conveys hydrogen prepared by the new energy base to each power plant in a high-pressure gaseous hydrogen storage manner; the pressure reducing valve group is used for reducing pressure of high-pressure gas-state stored hydrogen and then connecting the high-pressure gas-state stored hydrogen into the storage tank through the busbar, and an output port of the hydrogen pressure transfer equipment is connected into the hydrogen storage tank in the thermal power plant through the busbar after being subjected to pressure reduction through the pressure reducing valve group."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了火电厂灰氢的替代应用系统，其将火电厂氢源由新能源制氢替代有利于火电厂碳减排，助力实现“绿电制绿氢、产业用绿氢”的产业模式，提升火电厂对新能源消纳的价值。且氢源替代后，可消除现有氢气储罐压力容器，减少电厂压力容器相关检测工作。其包括：氢气压力转运设备；减压阀组；以及汇流排；所述氢气压力转运设备将新能源基地制取的氢气以高压气态储氢方式输送至各电厂；所述减压阀组将高压气态储氢减压后通过汇流排接入储罐中，所述氢气压力转运设备的输出口通过减压阀组减压后通过汇流排接入火电厂内的氢气储罐内。"
                }
            ]
        }
